room_title: Escape room "Murder of Crows" by Keynundrum in Topeka
room_address: 2900 SW Atwood, Suite C Topeka, KS 66614
room_description: As heir to the Crow estate, you have been tasked with searching your uncle's home for the missing deed and getting it to the executor before time runs out. This Edgar Allan Poe inspired room will challenge your whole team to explore his stories in ways you've never imagined.
